race.comment: Reve de Beylev mare HOUPETTE ROSE (10) raced from off the pace prior to finishing 4L third at this circuit. Selected to record her fifth win at this circuit. HELMA DE BUSSET (11) came home 1.75L clear of her rivals when racing at this track on her penultimate start. Expected to deliver another big effort. ILLUSTRE DE CHENOU (3) followed up a 2.5L triumph at Salon-de-Provence with a 1.25L fourth at Marseille-Borely. Strong claims of recording his fourth win of the year. Ulf du Noyer mare IRIS FROM (15) registered a solid effort finishing 4.25L fifth attempting a Class E Europeen event at Machecoul. One to note.
